HTML-FormHandler-Email-Template version 0.01002
============================================

This module allows you to easily and dynamically send templated emails from HTML::FormHandler forms.

Type the following after installing for more information

     perldoc HTML::FormHandler::Email::Template

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

Moose
Email::Sender::Simple
Email::Simple::Creator
Email::Sender::Transport::SMTP
Email::Simple
HTML::FormHandler::Email
HTML::FormHandler::Moose
HTML::FormHandler


